{"tid":1824058,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【入廁所避記者】廣東政協周星馳現身開會 建議大灣區培育創意人材","createTime":"2020-01-14T07:25:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T08:10:57.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"319afe1fbbba983856de7a38661f2c3622528298","tid":1824058,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T07:25:21.000Z","msg":"周星馳近日以廣東省政協委員身份去廣州開政協會議，他仍然是一頭銀白色長髮，戴著普通的深藍色棒球帽，打扮簡單樸素。久未露面的星爺有些老態，但據現場記者所見，他在場難得露出了不少笑容，跟許多行業內的人一起熱聊，開會時全程都在認真聽取大會發言。會後他準備離開現場時，媒體記者蜂擁而上，星爺一時無法脫身。<br />\n當星爺被問及今年帶來什麼提案，他指未來會有一系列創意人材培養計劃，也將此作為這次參會的主要想法。星爺表示：「在大灣區培訓創意人材是非常重要的事情，希望可以物色到更多創意人材，更進一步在國際市場發揮空間。」短短說了幾句，他就想離開，在助手的配合下，試圖擺脫記者，但未成功。最後，他只能躲進了廁所，媒體記者才知趣離開。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200114/large/1578979582_fafc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200114%2Flarge%2F1578979582_fafc.jpg&h=8f8de746&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200114/large/1578979362_b5f6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200114%2Flarge%2F1578979362_b5f6.jpg&h=7b0cce26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200114/large/1578979362_af51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200114%2Flarge%2F1578979362_af51.jpg&h=f1d7e1c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20200114/60483011\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200114%2F60483011&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSertEgU5aikFnqk5iyu2dsMw0%3D&h=94b22d00\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200114%2F60483011&h=5ccfb695\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https: